metadata.name: Mali, The last star collector
metadata.description:
In 3020, there is no longer sufficient power source in the world. 

Shining star is a new powerful resource that can be transform into any essential power for the world

Mali, a girl from Thai association astronaut partnership (TAAP) is the one who have special ability called “star collector” have to work with global partnership to find new power resource for humanity

Her mission is tracking the star position and lead her star collector team to access the area.
